{"tid":1188254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【名單不斷更新】更多小店加入罷市一天　籲 6.9 上街反送中","createTime":"2019-06-06T06:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T07:23:49.000Z","uid":184679,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"358ff3ab5e349c9f04d543c110256b01dd7a2af9","tid":1188254,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T06:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/store-07_InKMs_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fstore-07_InKMs_1200x0.png&h=b7903694&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6月9日（本周日）民陣將會發起反《逃犯條例》修訂遊行，有小店宣布當日休市一天，至今陸續有新的商店加入罷市行列。<br />\n<br />\n位於海怡半島的「嘉嫂辦館」宣布 6 月 9 日休息一天。店鋪在 Facebook 提到，「生意冇咗可以再做，香港冇咗，就連生意都冇得做！」，並在貼文中加上「自己香港自己救」的標籤。<br />\n<br />\n在小西灣的「叮叮老香港辦館」也在 Facebook 表示遊行當日會暫停營業一天，指出「今天不出來，以後出不來」，店鋪當日會與大家一起行，一起撐。<br />\n<br />\n香港 MG 戶外軍事用品店表示 6 月 9 日原定為銅鑼灣分店翻新後的首個營業日，但因為老闆認為當日「有一些更重要的事要去做」，故宣布銅鑼灣分店將會在當日休息，並附上「#守護我們的核心價值」、「 #守護我們的下一代」等標籤。<br />\n<br />\n位於銅鑼灣的 M2 Cafe 表示，不惜犧牲一日營業額，都決定要休息一天上街。Facebook 帖文指，小店員工及老闆都是土生土長香港人，「明知是雞蛋挑戰高牆」，但為香港的未來，必定會站出來對抗霸權。<br />\n<br />\n聯同較早前宣佈 6 月 9 日休業一天的旺角食肆基隆街五號、服裝店 UTRY、FORBRO 及觀塘服裝店 GALAXY，至今有最少 8 間小店在網上宣布將於反「送中」大遊行當日罷市。<br />\n<br />\n整理店鋪名單如下（持續更新中）：<br />\n<br />\n【旺角】基隆街五號<br />\n【旺角】UTRY<br />\n【觀塘】GALAXY<br />\n【旺角】FORBRO<br />\n【銅鑼灣】M2 Cafe<br />\n【銅鑼灣】香港MG戶外軍事用品店（銅鑼灣分店）<br />\n【小西灣】叮叮老香港辦館 Hong Kong Tram Store<br />\n【海怡半島】嘉嫂辦館‧ KASO Grocery<br />\n【深水埗】3C維修工作室<br />\n【網店】Littledreamer<br />\n【網店】Thai 型波衫 - 冷門球衣專門店<br />\n【油麻地】古迦玩具 Kuugatoys<br />\n【旺角】鬍鬚仔玩具 The Wuso【旺角】基隆街五號<br />\n【觀塘】Pepper Optical<br />\n【油麻地】in_111_<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%B7%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0-%E5%B0%8F%E5%BA%97%E9%99%B8%E7%BA%8C%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5%E7%BD%B7%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%A9-%E7%B1%B2-6-9-%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%97%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2596%25B7%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25BA%2597%25E9%2599%25B8%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E5%25B8%2582%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25A4%25A9-%25E7%25B1%25B2-6-9-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%2F&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2Bgibpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=c167ce19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2596%25B7%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25BA%2597%25E9%2599%25B8%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E5%25B8%2582%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25A4%25A9-%25E7%25B1%25B2-6-9-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%2F&h=6766fdf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%B7%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0-%E5%B0%8F%E5%BA%97%E9%99%B8%E7%BA%8C%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5%E7%BD%B7%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%A9-%E7%B1%B2-6-9-%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%97%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD/</a>"},{"pid":"27c70d4005cbe2252b8545d686641720d678864c","tid":1188254,"uid":226955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T06:54:26.000Z","msg":"全民反送中之餘，全世界都一樣反送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JTM23F0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJTM23F0.png&h=07d59843&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6月9號，全香港人一齊出嚟！"},{"pid":"19c8be6ef539bc60ff65d9776a91a5f35dc31670","tid":1188254,"uid":205937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T06:56:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"552a9852826de223b703f96d11d0c8cbf7bbd123","tid":1188254,"uid":103513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:43:23.000Z","msg":"哩兩日去幫襯下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal